OHIO VETERANS & FRATERNAL CHARITABLE COALITION
v.
YOST 2019-0016 Supreme Court of Ohio. June 3, 2019

CASE ANNOUNCEMENT

MOTION AND PROCEDURAL RULING

On joint motion to continue to hold in abeyance this court's determination on jurisdiction. Motion granted. The parties shall advise the court of the status of the negotiations within 90 days.
